<html lang="sk">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<title>Welcome</title>
		<style>
			@keyframes fadeIn {
				from {
					opacity: 0;
				}
				to {
					opacity: 1;
				}
			}

			@keyframes slideInLeft {
				from {
					opacity: 0;
					transform: translateX(-20px);
				}
				to {
					opacity: 1;
					transform: translateX(0);
				}
			}

			@keyframes slideInRight {
				from {
					opacity: 0;
					transform: translateX(20px);
				}
				to {
					opacity: 1;
					transform: translateX(0);
				}
			}

			body {
				font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fb 0%, #f3f1fa 50%, #faf7f5 100%);
				color: #111827;
				animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
			}

			.page-shell {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
				min-height: 100vh;
				gap: 24px;
				padding: 24px;
			}

			.sidebar {
				background: linear-gradient(180deg, #faf8f9 0%, #f5f3fa 100%);
				border: 1px solid #e8dfe5;
				border-radius: 18px;
				box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
				padding: 22px;
				animation: slideInLeft 0.8s ease-out;
			}

			.content {
				background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f9fef7 0%, #fef9fc 100%);
				border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
				border-radius: 18px;
				box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
				padding: 22px;
				animation: slideInRight 0.8s ease-out;
			}

			.sidebar h2 {
				margin-top: 0;
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.14em;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: #6b5b7d;
				border-bottom: 2px solid #d8c8e8;
				padding-bottom: 8px;
			}

			.widget {
				margin-top: 18px;
				padding: 16px;
				border-radius: 14px;
				background: #fef8fb;
				border: 1px solid #f0e5f0;
				animation: slideInLeft 0.8s ease-out;
				animation-fill-mode: both;
			}

			.widget:nth-child(2) {
				animation-delay: 0.1s;
			}

			.widget:nth-child(3) {
				animation-delay: 0.2s;
			}

			.widget:nth-child(4) {
				animation-delay: 0.3s;
			}

			.widget:nth-child(5) {
				animation-delay: 0.4s;
			}

			.widget:nth-child(6) {
				animation-delay: 0.5s;
			}

			.widget:nth-child(even) {
				background: #f8fef7;
				border-color: #e8f0e5;
			}

			.widget + .widget {
				margin-top: 14px;
			}

			.widget strong {
				display: block;
				margin-bottom: 10px;
				color: #6b5b7d;
			}

			.quick-links {
				padding-left: 1rem;
				margin: 0;
			}

			.quick-links li {
				margin: 10px 0;
				color: #475569;
			}

			.content h1 {
				color: #5a4a7d;
				border-bottom: 3px solid #d8c8e8;
				padding-bottom: 12px;
				animation: slideInRight 0.8s ease-out 0.1s both;
			}

			.content h2 {
				color: #6b5b7d;
				border-left: 4px solid #d8c8e8;
				padding-left: 12px;
				animation: slideInRight 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;
			}

			section {
				animation: slideInRight 0.8s ease-out;
				animation-fill-mode: both;
			}

			section:nth-of-type(1) {
				animation-delay: 0.3s;
			}

			section:nth-of-type(2) {
				animation-delay: 0.4s;
			}

			section:nth-of-type(3) {
				animation-delay: 0.5s;
			}

			section:nth-of-type(4) {
				animation-delay: 0.6s;
			}

			section:nth-of-type(5) {
				animation-delay: 0.7s;
			}

			.quick-links a,
			.content a {
				color: #8b6fb3;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			.quick-links a:hover,
			.content a:hover {
				color: #6b5b7d;
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="page-shell">
			<aside class="sidebar">
				<h2>Welcome Hub</h2>
				<p>Some typical welcome page extras for the first-time visitor.</p>

				<div class="widget">
					<strong>Latest update</strong>
					<p>We're rolling out a refreshed homepage experience with quick links, status updates, and friendly navigation.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="widget">
					<strong>Did you know?</strong>
					<ul>
						<li>Every page can be updated instantly with Astro.</li>
						<li>Sidebar widgets are great for announcements.</li>
						<li>Responsive layouts keep content readable on mobile.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="widget">
					<strong>Quick links</strong>
					<ul class="quick-links">
						<li><a href="/o-mne">O mne</a></li>
						<li><a href="https://github.com/hgivm1" target="_blank">GitHub</a></li>
						<li><a href="/contract">Contract</a></li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="widget">
					<strong>Featured Skills</strong>
					<ul class="quick-links">
						<li>Web Development</li>
						<li>UI/UX Design</li>
						<li>TypeScript & Astro</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="widget">
					<strong>Recent Activity</strong>
					<p>Site rebuilt with Astro for optimal performance and maintainability.</p>
				</div>
			</aside>

			<main class="content">
				<h1>Welcome</h1>
				<p>autor: <a href="https://github.com/hgivm1">hgivm1</a></p>
				<p>This site is a small personal welcome page built with Astro. It includes quick access to biography and contract details while keeping the layout clean and easy to navigate.</p>
				
				<section>
					<h2>About this page</h2>
					<p>Use the links in the sidebar to explore the profile page, contract overview, and other welcome content. The page is intentionally lightweight to help you focus on the most important information.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>What I Do</h2>
					<p>I'm a web developer and designer focused on creating clean, performant, and user-friendly digital experiences. My work spans from concept to deployment, with a strong emphasis on code quality and maintainability.</p>
					<p>Whether you need a professional website, custom web application, or technical consulting, I'm here to bring your vision to life.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>Technology Stack</h2>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>Frontend:</strong> Astro, TypeScript, React, HTML/CSS</li>
						<li><strong>Tools:</strong> Git, VS Code, Modern Build Tools</li>
						<li><strong>Approach:</strong> Performance-first, accessibility-focused, SEO-optimized</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>Why Astro?</h2>
					<p>This site is built with Astro because it offers incredible performance out of the box. Zero JavaScript by default, partial hydration for interactive components, and incredible developer experience make it perfect for modern web projects.</p>
				</section>
				
				<section>
					<h2>Next steps</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>Visit <a href="/o-mne">O mne</a> to learn more about the author.</li>
						<li>Open <a href="/contract">Contract</a> for general service and agreement details.</li>
						<li>Check out my <a href="https://github.com/hgivm1" target="_blank">GitHub</a> for code samples and projects.</li>
						<li>Check back often for updates as the site evolves.</li>
					</ul>
				</section>
			</main>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>	

